Class ElementsExtendedImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.jvm.java.plugin.adapter.ElementsExtendedImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ElementsExtended, Elements

    public class ElementsExtendedImpl
extends Object
implements ElementsExtended
    Wraps and extends Elements with methods that cannot be added as pure extension methods on MoreElements because they require per-instance state.
